        "answer": "A",
        "explanation": "$x = y/(y+5) \\implies xy + 5x = y \\implies 5x = y(1 - x) \\implies y = 5x/(1 - x)$."
      },
      {
        "type": "mcq",
        "question": "What is the remainder when $x^4 - 3x^2 + 2$ is divided by $x^2 + 1$?",
