        "answer": "A",
        "explanation": "$x^4 - 3x^2 + 2 = (x^2 - 4)(x^2 + 1) + 6$."
      },
      {
        "type": "mcq",
        "question": "Using synthetic division to divide $2x^3 - 5x^2 + 3x + 7$ by $x - 2$, what is the remainder?",
